Quote: Paunch dump hard to stomach..the paunch dump has been operating on trial for five months and Colyton residents say its smell and closeness to the Orua River is untenable. The paunch dump is run by Taranaki-based Global Vermiculture Ltd.. Mr Hocken found out about the paunch dump from the council.
