Quote: Its paunch dump has been operating on trial for five months in the Manawatu, collecting the intestinal contents of dead livestock from meatworks and drying it for feeding to worms .. He contacted the regional council which was 'reasonably sympathetic' about the problem, and disclosed the existence of the paunch dump.
